<B>__{brad}
<A>__{he comes pounding down a slope, and he takes off his hat and skims it away. he rips off a neckerchief as though to relieve the rush of raging blood.}
<L>__{92 b exterior the edge of a rise med. close shot brad night}
<A>__{he reaches the crest and reins in. a distant firelight is on his face. he takes one moment to look down into the comanche camp o.s. then he has his gun out. his eyes are wild, his face wet with sweat. then he throws back his head and he yells and with the yell goes charging into the camp.}
